                  <body xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:xfa="http://www.xfa.org/schema/xfa-data/1.0/"><p style="font-size:8pt;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span>1. In case of any discrepancies, please contact DelVal USA office. If no response is received within the next 48 hours, we will consider<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">  </span>this invoice accepted.</p><p style="font-size:8pt;letter-spacing:0in"><span style="xfa-spacerun:yes"> </span>2.<span style="xfa-spacerun:yes">  </span>This is an electronic invoice copy. No signature is required.</p></body>
